OL,3,CEngland v Norway: What time is kick
OL,4,Coff and what are the major hurdles?
OL,6,FOn Saturday, England will take on
OL,7,FNorway in in the quarter-finals of the
OL,8,F2026 Fifa World Cup.
OL,10,FFollowing their win against hosts
OL,11,FMexico at Azteca Stadium, the Three
OL,12,FLions are hoping to beat the
OL,13,FScandinavians to bag a spot in semi
OL,14,Ffinals.
OL,16,FHere's what you need to know ahead of
OL,17,Fthe crucial game.
OL,19,FWhat time is kick off and will pubs be
OL,20,Fopen in England?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
