OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1783696744
OL,3,CEngland v Norway: What time is kick
OL,4,Coff and what are the major hurdles?
OL,6,FThe England v Norway game, weather
OL,7,Fdepending, is set to start at 10pm
OL,8,F(BST) and pubs in England will be
OL,9,Fallowed to remain open for the full
OL,10,Fmatch.
OL,12,FWhilst provisions were made separately
OL,13,Ffor the England v Mexico game which
OL,14,Fhad a later kick-off time, matches
OL,15,Fthat start between 9pm and 10pm in the
OL,16,FUK can be enjoyed in the pub until 2am.
OL,18,FNorway's golden striker
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
