OL,3,CEngland v Norway: What time is kick
OL,4,Coff and what are the major hurdles?
OL,6,FGolden haired striker Erling Haaland
OL,7,Fis a Golden Boot contender, who was
OL,8,Falso Norway's golden ticket into the
OL,9,Fquarter-finals.
OL,11,FHe could prove tough competition for
OL,12,Fthe Three Lions.
OL,14,FHaaland, who is appearing at his first
OL,15,FWorld Cup, is already Norway's record
OL,16,Fscorer with 62 goals, almost doubling
OL,17,FJorgen Juve's previous record of 33,
OL,18,Fdespite only making his debut in 2019.
OL,26,@yD@Bo|
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
