OL,3,CEngland v Norway: What time is kick
OL,4,Coff and what are the major hurdles?
OL,6,FThe Manchester City star, 25, was
OL,7,Fresponsible for both goals in Norway's
OL,8,F2-1 match against Brazil on Sunday.
OL,10,FBoth Haaland and England striker Harry
OL,11,FKane are in competition for the top
OL,12,Fscorer honour as the tournament
OL,13,Freaches the quarter-final stage.
OL,15,FArgentina's Lionel Messi leads the way
OL,16,Fon eight goals, Haaland shares second
OL,17,Fplace on seven with France star Kylian
OL,18,FMbappe ` with Kane just a goal further
OL,19,Fbehind on six.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
