OL,3,CEngland v Norway: What time is kick
OL,4,Coff and what are the major hurdles?
OL,6,FHaaland, having sat out Norway's final
OL,7,FGroup I game against France, has
OL,8,Fplayed a game fewer than his rivals.
OL,10,FHe scored twice in each of the wins
OL,11,Fover Iraq, Senegal and Brazil, and
OL,12,Fonce against the Ivory Coast.
OL,14,FAs the competition heats up, so does
OL,15,Fthe weather in Miami
OL,17,FOn Thursday, South Florida's weather
OL,18,Fservice expanded its heat advisory to
OL,19,Fthe whole region.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
