OL,3,CEngland v Norway: What time is kick
OL,4,Coff and what are the major hurdles?
OL,6,FThe Met Office predicts a high of 34C
OL,7,Flooking ahead to Saturday, with the UV
OL,8,Flevel tipping into the "extreme"
OL,9,Fcategory.
OL,11,FHowever, humidity levels could even
OL,12,Fpush the temperature to feel closer to
OL,13,F43C.
OL,15,FFifa's rules also mean that if the
OL,16,Ftemperature rises above 32 degrees,
OL,17,Fmatch organisers should consider extra
OL,18,Fprecautions to prevent player illness
OL,19,Fdue to the heat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
