OL,3,CEngland v Norway: What time is kick
OL,4,Coff and what are the major hurdles?
OL,6,FThere are also some concerns
OL,7,Fsurrounding the possibility of thunder
OL,8,Fand lightning being predicted in Miami
OL,9,Faround kick-off time.
OL,11,FAccording to Fifa, lightning that
OL,12,Fstrikes within 13km of the venue will
OL,13,Fcause disruption to the game.
OL,15,FMonday's Mexico v England clash was
OL,16,Ffaced with controversial timing
OL,17,Fdisruption in the lead up, although
OL,18,Fultimately was only delayed by an hour.
OL,20,FYellow cards could cause problems for
OL,21,FEngland
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
