OL,3,CEngland v Norway: What time is kick
OL,4,Coff and what are the major hurdles?
OL,6,FEngland are in a somewhat unstable
OL,7,Fposition when it comes to discipline,
OL,8,Fwith some players in danger of
OL,9,Freceiving a one-match ban, should they
OL,10,Fpick up a second yellow card on
OL,11,FSaturday.
OL,13,FWhilst yellow cards from the group-
OL,14,Fstage hove now been effectively wiped,
OL,15,FWorld Cup rules say players who are
OL,16,Fgiven two yellow cards overall across
OL,17,Fthe final 32, 16 and quarter-finals
OL,18,Fwill be suspended.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
