OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1783696744
OL,3,CEngland v Norway: What time is kick
OL,4,Coff and what are the major hurdles?
OL,6,FSuspensions last one game, so if a
OL,7,Fplayer receives their second yellow
OL,8,Fcard during the England v Norway
OL,9,Fmatch, and their team wins, they would
OL,10,Fbe reprimanded by missing the semi-
OL,11,Ffinals.
OL,13,FFour of the key England players have
OL,14,Falready received yellow cards, putting
OL,15,Fthem further at risk of a ban.
OL,17,FOn Sunday's victory against Mexico,
OL,18,FArsenal midfielder Declan Rice was
OL,19,Fcautioned less than a minute in.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
