OL,11,FMarc Guehi and Nico O'Reilly, both
OL,12,FManchester City players, were also
OL,13,Fgiven a yellow card each in the same
OL,14,Fgame.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, England star Jude
OL,17,FBellingham, who was given player of
OL,18,Fthe match against Mexico, was booked
OL,19,F19 minutes into England's winning
OL,20,Fmatch against DR Congo.
