OL,3,CEngland v Norway: What time is kick
OL,4,Coff and what are the major hurdles?
OL,6,FJarell Quansah was sent off with a
OL,7,Fcontroversial red card in the 54th
OL,8,Fminute of the Mexico game.
OL,10,FNorway fans and the viral 'Viking Row'
OL,12,FNorway may have made history by
OL,13,Freaching the last eight for the first
OL,14,Ftime at the World Cup, but it is not
OL,15,Fjust their performance that has been
OL,16,Fmaking waves at the tournament.
OL,18,FNorway's unique celebration has taken
OL,19,Fover social media and captured the
OL,20,Fimagination of football fans around
OL,21,Fthe world.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
