PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1783696744
OL,3,CEngland v Norway: What time is kick
OL,4,Coff and what are the major hurdles?
OL,6,FWhile England have celebrated their
OL,7,Fwins with rousing fan-led sing-a-longs
OL,8,Fof Oasis' Wonderwall, Norway have
OL,9,Fleant into the country's Viking
OL,10,Fheritage.
OL,12,FThe 'Viking row' celebration involves
OL,13,Flarge groups of fans performing a
OL,14,Fsynchronised seated movement that
OL,15,Fmimics rowing a ship to the beat of a
OL,16,Fdrum.
OL,18,FSupporters often wear Viking helmets
OL,19,Fpaired with the team's red-and-blue
OL,20,Fjerseys and row in unison to the
OL,21,Fsteady beat of the drum.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
